  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of mischievous aliens mesmerized by the sport of boxing as they battle it out all over our beloved planet Earth, unaware of the laws and traditions of human society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the chaos and whimsy of simulated characters and environments in this action arena brawler that will keep you hooked with surprising combat twists and gameplay variety. Board the spaceship, we're off to the next scrimmage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/c61e7a11e5939a481e15d3da695d9ce1.webp?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIMULATED CHAOS</strong> - Take control of funny, physics based alien fighters and use crazy power ups to turn the tide of battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.poster.avif?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.webm?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.mp4?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARENA COMBAT</strong> - Fight to dominate in different levels, each with their own quirks and hazards.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/13b36076aad2d24d76f0113a3c33e828.poster.avif?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/13b36076aad2d24d76f0113a3c33e828.webm?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/13b36076aad2d24d76f0113a3c33e828.mp4?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ONLINE AND LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong> - Battle it out against players around the globe or invite your friends to local multiplayer matches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/6464e3da6bc52156350bb0d8d8dae89e.avif?t=1732699158\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras_big/6464e3da6bc52156350bb0d8d8dae89e.avif?t=1732699158 width=800 height=408 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMISATION</strong> - Unlock new player skins, gloves and name tags to customize your characters and stunt on your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/b50ef9c226aed594b73eba705db4a822.poster.avif?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/b50ef9c226aed594b73eba705db4a822.webm?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/b50ef9c226aed594b73eba705db4a822.mp4?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/c61e7a11e5939a481e15d3da695d9ce1.webp?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of mischievous aliens mesmerized by the sport of boxing as they battle it out all over our beloved planet Earth, unaware of the laws and traditions of human society.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the chaos and whimsy of simulated characters and environments in this action arena brawler that will keep you hooked with surprising combat twists and gameplay variety. Board the spaceship, we're off to the next scrimmage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/c61e7a11e5939a481e15d3da695d9ce1.webp?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=27 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SIMULATED CHAOS</strong> - Take control of funny, physics based alien fighters and use crazy power ups to turn the tide of battle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.poster.avif?t=1732699158\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.webm?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/e591dce6b94f49ac8e35a4ee78b19283.mp4?t=1732699158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARENA COMBAT</strong> - Fight to dominate in different levels, each with their own quirks and hazards.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1186660/extras/13b36076aad2d2